As quickly as Amber Heard and Johnny Depp burned bright, they just as speedily split up. Although their marriage lasted just 15 months, the battle in courts and in the court of public opinion continued. Audiotapes have recently leaked online that show that Amber actually abused him. But where did all of this begin and how did it come to that?
